[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "电梯门缓缓闭合，最后的狭缝中，我看到了龙舌兰回过头，冲我露出一个微笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "下一刻，子弹、爆炸声，连同龙舌兰、长乐和伊格妮丝的怒吼都被隔绝在门外，而电梯毫不留念地快速下降，将我带往这座建筑的最底层。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "漫长的等待中，忽闪忽闪的电梯灯和吱呀作响的电梯缆绳似乎在向我讲述，最底层已经许久没有人前往。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "最终，它稳稳停下，一条狭长的走道随即出现在我的眼前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里是这个大厅唯一的出入口，一切事件的幕后黑手，被称为“幽影”的宿敌，已经无处可逃了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我握紧了手中的枪，朝着深处走去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而，当我进入大厅中心，却发现这里一个人都没有。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不对吧，为什么会一个人都没有？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃……这个，其实是因为，幽影的扮演者还没找到。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "幽影不就是那个人偶吗？刚才的战斗片段中，它的演出效果还挺好的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那是幽影的战斗形态，总不能用它来和夜魇骑士演对手戏吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "先用人类形态阐述自己的理念，再变成怪物战斗，这才是正常的剧情展开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "枫",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "第四幕第三场，导演忘了找演员，需要特效支持……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "前半句就不用记了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我是不是应该配合一下这个冷笑话？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这不是什么大问题！本来我也打算用特效来实现变身的效果，分析员大人，你就先对着空气发挥演技吧！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有些太难为我了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过，我当然也准备好了备用计划。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "小枫！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "枫",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎哎？怎、怎么了，导演？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "粉头发的少女连忙收起笔记本，一脸困惑地看向龙舌兰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就由你来扮演幽影吧！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "枫",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我演幽影？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没错，我想了很久，果然还是你比较合适。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也太随便了。你看，小枫都被吓到说不出话了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "枫",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我我我……我愿意！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "枫",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "抱歉！我太激动了！能和playername英雄阁下一起演戏，我很荣幸！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她看着我的眼睛，眼里似乎都要冒出星星了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……我早该想到，小枫她毕竟是龙舌兰带出来的，很难不被龙舌兰一贯的风格影响。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "龙舌兰1",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "总之，我先陪小枫就先熟悉一下台词，讲一下演绎风格，大家做好拍摄准备，我们半小时以后开工！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "离开电梯后，我握紧了手中的枪，沿着通道，朝着深处走去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "数十步后，眼见通道便到了尽头。而在大厅中心，一个人影孤身站立着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在昏暗的灯光下，对方的年龄、性别和服饰，我都无从得知。只能勉强看到那人正背对着大厅的入口，将身后毫无防备地暴露出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "要做的事情很简单。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "举起手枪",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的同伴们还在为我争取时间，所以我不会给对方反应的机会。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "扣下扳机，枪声响起。子弹精准地沿着枪口与对方头部连成的线射出——却直直穿了过去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么可能！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我忍不住骂了一句，难道“幽影”真的无法受到攻击吗？！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，不对，冷静下来，对方应该只是利用这里的环境，以我难以捕捉到的速度闪过了子弹。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "“幽影”",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呵……偷袭可不是绅士的行径。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你？！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "听到“幽影”的声音，我忽然一怔。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "“幽影”",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "play_Vo_dlc10ep7_Kaede_01",
        "zh_CN": "别那么心急嘛，“英雄大人”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "“幽影”",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "play_Vo_dlc10ep7_Kaede_02",
        "zh_CN": "起码，先让我把舞台的灯光打开吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "两束聚光灯分别打到了我们身上，我终于得以看清对方的样貌。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "理所当然的，与我所想的完全不同，但这也说明不了什么……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员夜魇",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你已经无路可逃了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
