    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "“幽影”",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Vo_dlc10ep7_Kaede_06",
        "zh_CN": "躲在这个虚假的名字后面，你手上的鲜血，真的比我更少吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "“幽影”",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Vo_dlc10ep7_Kaede_07",
        "zh_CN": "黑暗中的英雄，不早就是，黑暗的一部分了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "“幽影”",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Vo_dlc10ep7_Kaede_08",
        "zh_CN": "……你说对吧，海姆达尔的分析员？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "“幽影”",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Vo_dlc10ep7_Kaede_09",
        "zh_CN": "罗赞司令向您问好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伴随着震耳的枪声，我眼见高速旋转的子弹从枫的手枪中射出。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我反应过来的时候，胸口已经被洞穿，绽出了一朵血花。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈，这绝对不是道具枪的威力……伴随着这样毫无意义的念头，我的眼前逐渐模糊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然后，重重倒在了地上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
